{"tid":2429606,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：國安案疲勞轟炸 誤傷控方有點不理想","createTime":"2021-03-02T12:24:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T12:27:02.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9e4fc606056fd25a541f0d864953cc339547d673","tid":2429606,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:24:55.000Z","msg":"民主派被控違國安案32人完成保釋陳詞 休庭35分鐘<br />\n<br />\n47名發起或參與去年民主派初選人士，被控「串謀顛覆國家政權罪」，案件繼續提堂。<br />\n<br />\n至晚上約7時，暫時約有32名被告經代表律師，完成申請保釋的陳詞。國安法指定法官蘇惠德安排暫時休庭約35分鐘，讓控辯雙方及被告用膳。之後會繼續進行餘下被告的保釋申請。<br />\n<br />\n蘇惠德今日較早前說，今日的審訊時間最多可能直至晚上10時，同意審訊時間太夜並不理想。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578371-20210302.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578371-20210302.htm&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA5j7jGrzIfagxCK2eNaONkM%3D&h=860f85cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578371-20210302.htm&h=1f9841c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578371-20210302.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7e84c03b674b38f43613194939ef8da492428558","tid":2429606,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:27:02.000Z","msg":"法律唔係無差別咩？"}]}